---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import site from '@/lib/site';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Immunity Support IV Therapy | Menon Medispa | Millburn, NJ"
  description="Immunity support IV drip therapy in Millburn NJ. Strengthen your body's natural defenses with our customized immune-boosting infusions."
>
  <main class="sp" data-slug="immunity-support">

    <section class="sp-hero" aria-label="Immunity Support IV Therapy in Millburn NJ">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div class="sp-hero__grid">
          <div class="sp-hero__content">
            <h1 class="sp-hero__title">Immunity Support IV Therapy in Millburn NJ</h1>
            <p class="sp-hero__eyebrow">Strengthen Your Defenses from the Inside Out.</p>
            <p class="sp-hero__lead">Don't wait until you're sick to support your immune system. Our Immunity Support IV drip in Millburn, NJ, delivers a powerful dose of immune-boosting nutrients directly to your bloodstream to help you stay well and recover faster.</p>
            <div class="sp-hero__actions">
              <a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold" href="/consultation">Book Your IV Therapy</a>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-reviews">
              <div class="sp-reviews__avatars">
                <img src="/images/90411e0041df.png" alt="Client review" width="44" height="44" />
                <img src="/images/305afeda5f9a.png" alt="Client review" width="44" height="44" />
                <img src="/images/b95880091b44.png" alt="Client review" width="44" height="44" />
              </div>
              <div class="sp-reviews__text">
                <span class="sp-reviews__stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</span>
                <span class="sp-reviews__count">100+ 5 Star Reviews</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <img class="sp-hero__img" src="/images/651c7c197b52.png" alt="Immunity Support IV Therapy in Millburn NJ" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-badges" aria-label="Highlights">
      <div class="sp-container sp-badges__row">
        <p class="sp-badge"><span class="sp-badge__check">&#10003;</span> Boost Your Immunity</p>
        <p class="sp-badge"><span class="sp-badge__check">&#10003;</span> Fight Seasonal Illness</p>
        <p class="sp-badge"><span class="sp-badge__check">&#10003;</span> Faster Recovery</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-plain" aria-label="Formulas">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;">
          <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(1.75rem,3vw,2.25rem);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 1.5rem;">Choose Your Formula</h2>
          <div style="background:#f8f4f0;padding:1.5rem;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
            <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-xl);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.4rem;">IMMUNITY Signature</h3>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);font-style:italic;color:#6a6470;margin:0 0 0.75rem;font-size:var(--text-sm);">Best for a potent, targeted immune boost to stay healthy during peak seasons.</p>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0 0 0.75rem;line-height:1.7;">This drip is packed with a powerful blend of essential vitamins and minerals to form the foundation of your immune health.</p>
            <ul style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;line-height:1.8;padding-left:1.5rem;margin:0;"><li>Vitamin C: A high-dose, powerful antioxidant that is essential for the function of immune cells and helps fight oxidative stress.</li><li>Zinc: A critical mineral that is directly involved in the development and function of immune cells, helping your body mount an effective defense.</li><li>Glutathione: Your body's most powerful natural antioxidant, protecting immune cells from damage and keeping them functioning at their peak.</li></ul>
          </div><div style="background:#f8f4f0;padding:1.5rem;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
            <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-xl);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.4rem;">IMMUNITY Deluxe</h3>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);font-style:italic;color:#6a6470;margin:0 0 0.75rem;font-size:var(--text-sm);">Best for comprehensive, long-term immune strengthening and overall wellness.</p>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0 0 0.75rem;line-height:1.7;">This all-in-one formula provides a full-spectrum immune boost to optimize your entire immune system. Includes the Signature foundation, plus:</p>
            <ul style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;line-height:1.8;padding-left:1.5rem;margin:0;"><li>Complete B-Complex: Essential B vitamins that support cellular energy production, ensuring your immune cells have the fuel they need to function.</li><li>Magnesium: Supports hundreds of biochemical reactions in the body, including those essential for a healthy immune response.</li><li>Full Spectrum Minerals: A comprehensive mineral blend that provides all the micronutrients your immune system needs to operate optimally.</li></ul>
          </div>
          <p style="margin-top:2rem;"><a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold" href="/consultation">Schedule Now</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-photos" aria-label="Customer Photos">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div class="sp-photos__head"><h2>Hear From Our Customers!</h2></div>
        <div class="sp-photos__grid">
          <img src="/images/9ebaca3843d3.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/6c461885a28e.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/823792ea5ead.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/cd675890fe0d.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/images/2e5d1e68225a.jpg" alt="IV Therapy customer" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-plain sp-plain--alt" aria-label="Process">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;">
          <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(1.75rem,3vw,2.25rem);color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 1.5rem;">Simple, Relaxing, and Effective</h2>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;">
            <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;">
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-2xl);color:var(--color-accent-warm);flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;">01</span>
              <div><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.25rem;">Personalized Consultation</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0;line-height:1.7;">Your session begins with a brief consultation with one of our registered nurses. They will review your wellness goals and answer any questions to ensure your treatment is perfectly suited to your needs.</p></div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;">
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-2xl);color:var(--color-accent-warm);flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;">02</span>
              <div><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.25rem;">Relax and Recharge</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0;line-height:1.7;">Once settled in our comfortable therapy lounge, the IV drip is administered. The process is virtually painless and takes about 45-60 minutes. You can relax, read, or catch up on emails while your body absorbs the nutrients.</p></div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;">
              <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:var(--text-2xl);color:var(--color-accent-warm);flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;">03</span>
              <div><h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;color:var(--color-ink);margin:0 0 0.25rem;">Feel the Benefits</h3><p style="font-family:var(--font-ui);color:#5e5e5e;margin:0;line-height:1.7;">Many clients report immediate benefits after their session. The nutrients continue to work for days, supporting your body's natural processes and helping you feel and look your best.</p></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-pricing" aria-label="Pricing">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div class="sp-pricing__head">
          <h2>Book Your IV Therapy</h2>
          <p style="font-style:italic;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">All IV Drips are 500ml. Upgrade to 1000ml for only $25</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sp-pricelist">
          <div class="sp-priceitem">
            <img class="sp-priceitem__thumb" src="/images/651c7c197b52.png" alt="IMMUNITY (Signature)" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="sp-priceitem__main">
              <a class="sp-priceitem__title" href="/booking-calendar/immunity-signature">IMMUNITY (Signature)</a>
              <p class="sp-priceitem__sub">500ml.</p>
              <a class="sp-priceitem__readmore" href="/service-page/immunity-signature">Read More</a>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-priceitem__price">$200</div>
            <a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold sp-priceitem__cta" href="/booking-calendar/immunity-signature">Request to Book</a>
          </div>
          <div class="sp-priceitem">
            <img class="sp-priceitem__thumb" src="/images/651c7c197b52.png" alt="IMMUNITY (Deluxe)" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="sp-priceitem__main">
              <a class="sp-priceitem__title" href="/booking-calendar/immunity-deluxe">IMMUNITY (Deluxe)</a>
              <p class="sp-priceitem__sub">500ml.</p>
              <a class="sp-priceitem__readmore" href="/service-page/immunity-deluxe">Read More</a>
            </div>
            <div class="sp-priceitem__price">$250</div>
            <a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold sp-priceitem__cta" href="/booking-calendar/immunity-deluxe">Request to Book</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-testimonial" aria-label="What Our Clients Say">
      <img class="sp-testimonial__bg" src="/images/30cfb9e87c60.png" alt="" width="1440" height="626" loading="lazy" />
      <div class="sp-testimonial__overlay"></div>
      <div class="sp-container sp-testimonial__inner">
        <h2 class="sp-script-title sp-script-title--light" style="margin-bottom:2rem;">What Our <em>Clients</em> Say</h2>
        <blockquote class="sp-quote">
          <span class="sp-quote__mark">&ldquo;</span>
          Jennifer is amazing. Her aura and energy makes you feel welcomed and comfortable. Love our sessions! And my girl Rose Marie, the receptionist, is just lovely! I always leave with great joy after seeing them.
          <cite>Alexa C.</cite>
        </blockquote>
        <img src="/images/5be44787b3a9.png" alt="5 Star Google Reviews" width="143" height="74" loading="lazy" style="margin-top:1.75rem;" />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-faq" aria-label="Frequently asked questions">
      <div class="sp-container">
        <div class="sp-faq__card">
          <div class="sp-faq__head"><h2 class="sp-faq__title">Frequently asked questions</h2></div>
          <div class="sp-faq__list">
            <details class="sp-faq__item" open>
              <summary>Can IV therapy actually prevent me from getting sick?</summary>
              <div class="sp-faq__answer"><p>While no treatment can guarantee you won't get sick, IV therapy significantly strengthens your body's natural defenses. High-dose vitamin C and zinc have been clinically shown to reduce the severity and duration of illness, and maintaining strong nutritional levels supports optimal immune function.</p></div>
            </details>
            <details class="sp-faq__item">
              <summary>How quickly does the Immunity IV drip work?</summary>
              <div class="sp-faq__answer"><p>The nutrients are delivered directly to your bloodstream, bypassing the digestive system for 100% bioavailability. Many clients feel a boost in energy and wellness within hours of their session, and your immune system is better equipped to fight infection immediately.</p></div>
            </details>
            <details class="sp-faq__item">
              <summary>Should I get the IV therapy when I'm already sick?</summary>
              <div class="sp-faq__answer"><p>Absolutely. Our IV therapy can significantly accelerate your recovery by flooding your body with the nutrients your immune system needs most when it's fighting an infection. High-dose Vitamin C and Zinc are particularly effective at shortening illness duration.</p></div>
            </details>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sp-cta" aria-label="Protect Your Health Year-Round">
      <div class="sp-container sp-cta__grid">
        <div class="sp-cta__copy">
          <h2 class="sp-cta__title">Protect Your Health Year-Round</h2>
          <p class="sp-cta__sub">Menon Medispa Millburn NJ</p>
          <p>Take a proactive approach to your wellness. Schedule your Immunity Support IV therapy at Menon Medispa in Millburn, NJ today.</p>
          <a class="sp-btn sp-btn--gold" href="/consultation">Schedule Free Consultation</a>
        </div>
        <div class="sp-cta__media">
          <img src="/images/b1a819f35921.webp" alt="Menon Office Staff" width="431" height="560" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</BaseLayout>
